result.name: strategic-industrial-locations-udp-june-2006-rochdale-borough-council
result.notes:
Strategic industrial locations are a series of allocations relating to the Rochdale UDP June 2006.  These allocations cover planning policies on employment and the economy (Chapter 8):
EC/2 – Primary employment zones (allocations of the primary employment zones)
EC/3 – Mixed employment zones (allocations of the mixed employment zones)
EC/7 – Kingsway Business Park (allocation of Kingsway Business Park)
EC/8 – Development sites in employment zones (allocations of development sites in employment zones)
EC/9 – Sandbrook Park (allocation of Sandbrook Park)
